Our financings are typically secured against our assets. Since the security we provide is on a pari-passu basis to all lenders (except to NHB, which is on exclusive charge basis), we are required to obtain no-objection letters or pari-passu letters from the perfection of security from all our lenders every time we raise new secured borrowing, which is time-consuming.

